The masks cover the nose and mouth effectively, minimizing the risk of viral transmission.The black color not only adds a touch of style but also helps in concealing any dirt or stains that may accumulate over time. This discreet feature is especially appreciated when wearing the mask for extended periods.The pack of 100 ensures that we have an ample supply of masks on hand, allowing for regular replacement and ensuring we are always equipped with fresh, clean masks. This is essential for maintaining optimal protection.The disposable nature of these masks is a convenient and hygienic solution. It eliminates the need for constant washing and drying, reducing the risk of contamination and ensuring that we always have a clean mask available.These masks have become an integral part of our daily routine. Whether it's a trip to the grocery store or a visit to the doctor's office, we feel a sense of security knowing we have reliable face masks at our disposal.In terms of value, the 100Pcs Black Disposable Face Masks offer exceptional cost-effectiveness. The pack provides a generous supply that lasts for an extended period, making it a practical and economical choice for everyday use.In summary, these face masks have become an indispensable part of our lives in the era of Covid-19. They provide essential protection without sacrificing comfort or style. If you're in search of reliable disposable masks, this pack is a five-star choice that I wholeheartedly recommend to anyone prioritizing their health and safety.

reviews.reviewText: I received my masks neatly packaged in 2 packs of 50. They were sealed tightly, almost airless, which is good to keep stuff out!I opened one pack hoping they didn't smell badly like other reviewers said, & thankfully they had NO smell. Totally odorless.They are lightweight, breathable & as comfortable as these things can be. The ear loops are soft & stretch enough to fit most. The fabric isn't super soft, but it isn't rough, nor does it have those itchy fibers I've had in other masks.I am a hairdresser & have to wear a mask all day, 8 to 12 hours, so I really need a mask that I can breath through, & one that doesn't itch my face all day! These are great for me.They are, indeed, 3 layers & offer as much protection as other masks of this type, I would imagine. I've been using this kind of mask for a year + now with no issues. These are exactly like the ones I got from Costco, only those were $10 for 50 masks, where here I got 100 for $11. A much better value.This is my experience& I hope this helps you decide if these are right for you.
